headline: Robinhood Takes Aim At One Of Charles Schwab's Remaining Bastions
summary: The Schwab rival tied new acquisition to looming wealth transfer, which should benefit its core millennial customers.

headline: Interactive Brokers Launches Plan d’Epargne en Actions (PEA Classique) Accounts
summary: GREENWICH, Conn., November 20, 2024--Interactive Brokers (Nasdaq: IBKR), an automated global electronic broker, announced the launch of Plan d’Epargne en Actions accounts.
